data.description: TOTALLY REMODELED AND MOVE IN CONDITION 3 BEDROOM KENMORE HOME.  Beautifully appointed and tastefully done.  NEW Hot water tank, A/C Unit and Heater.  Plus all NEW Electric wiring & service throughout the home! All new floor coverings, new paint, remodeled kitchen and baths.  High End SMART kitchen appliances are INCLUDED.  New Granite counter tops are stunning! HUGE full attic that could easily be finished into living space.  The basement, is dry and immaculate.  There is even a front enclosed 3 season porch! Don't miss the garden sitting area along the garage too and the balcony off the Master Bedroom!  Seller says to BRING OFFERS.  You don't want to miss this one!
